race.comment: HOW WE GO (1) missed the frame last time but just three runs back was a strong Restricted WIN winner (16.28) at this track over 278m. Has the ability and can find winning form this time. CHOCOLATE'S CAN (2) has a strong record this journey with five wins and a minor from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (26.61) when eighth over 461m at Hobart in a Grade 4/5. Can feature with the right run. MADE UP STORIES (4) boasts a strong record this journey with five wins and two minors from 12 tries. Below best last time at this track (16.49) in a Grade 4, finishing a 4 length fifth. Looks well placed here and among the chances. TIMELESS GRACIE (7) is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time. Something for the Multiples: ROJO MOLLY (3)
